'''Firmina''' (201-158) ( s [[Tifinaɣ]] ⴼⵉⵔⵎⵉⵏⴰ )  d mmi-s n ugellid [[Sifaks]] . Tebḍa Ruma tagelda n baba-s gar-as d [[Mass-nsen|Masensen]] . Tefka-as [[Lmasisil]] tagelda n baba-s .

== Tudert ==
Fermina d mmi-s n uɛedaw n yirumaniyen yuwi-d seg-s karuh-is d reffu-ines  , ɣas akken fkan-as Lmasisil ur tebɣin i [[Mass-nsen|Masensen]] ameddakel-nsen . Imi llan ugaden lukzn ad yegled [[Mass-nsen|Masensen]] Masilya d Masisilya ad asen-iruḥ aṭas n usirem deg Tefriqt . Maca mallan sin n yigeldunen imaziɣen ulac tuggdi , imi ad d-ggrin di ccwal kan . 

Ur d-nufi ara ayen nniḍen deg tudert n ugellid-agi d wayen yexdem ass mi yella . ur d-nufi daɣen awalen ɣef taggara-s kra n yimazranen nan-d belli Masensen yegled masilya d Masisilya deg useggas n 158 iban belli deg useggas agi i yeɣli Firmina , imi ur nesli s ugellid n Masisilya anagar [[Mass-nsen|Masensen]] ; yeǧǧa-d yiwen n mmi-s d ageldun qqaren-as [[Arxubazan]] 

Akka i teɣli ccetla n [[Sifaks]] .
